title: Na Fianna (band)
text:
Na Fianna are an Irish band, with members Ciar√°n Finn, Hugh Finn, Peter McMahon and James O'Connor. The current members are successors to the group which were runners-up in the second season of the All Ireland Talent Show TV series in 2010. The original group was first formed in March 2007.
